high_descs: turn around and head forward, take a right at the fridge then a left to face the counter the is to the right of the fridge
Pick up the white coffee mug that is sitting on the counter
Turn left and walk to the fridge, then turn right and face the fridge
Open the fridge and place the white coffee mug into the freezer then close the door. Then open the fridge and pick up the coffee mug that is in the freezer and close the door
Take a step backward and continue to face the fridge
Open the cabinet that is under the counter directly to the right of the fridge and place the coffee mug inside the cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a cold mug into a cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and go right and then turn to face the counter on the left where the lettuce and mug is.
Pick the mug up from the counter.
Go to the left and face the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and then pick the cup up again.
Back up and face the lower cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Open the lower cabinet to the right of the fridge and put the cup in it and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the fridge and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the white mug to the right of the head of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the mug inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, walk forward and turn around to face the cabinets next to the fridge.
Open the lower cabinet to the right of the fridge, put the chilled mug inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a cabinet.
